Package umlcodeconverter.element

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConstructorConverter
    Provides a static method to convert UmlOperations of an UmlElement to CodeConstructors and adding them to the CodeElement
    ConstructorConverterTest
    Tests the ConstructorConverter.
    ElementConverter
    Class providing static methods to convert UmlElements to CodeElements and adding them to a CodeParent.
    ElementConverterTest
    Tests the ElementConverter.
    FieldConverter
    Class providing a static method to convert the UmlAttributes of a given UmlElement to CodeFields and adding them to the CodeElement
    FieldConverterTest
    Tests the FieldConverter.
    LiteralConverter
    Provides a static method to convert the UmlLiterals of an UmlEnumeration to CodeLiterals
    LiteralConverterTest
    Tests the LiteralConverter
    MethodConverter
    Provides a static method to convert UmlOperations of an UmlElement to CodeMethods and adding them to the CodeElement
    MethodConverterTest
    Tests the MethodConverter.
    ModifierConverter
    Class providing a static method to convert a UmlVisibility to a CodeVisibility
    ModifierConverterTest
    Tests the ModifierConverter.
    ParameterConverter
    Provides a static method to convert UmlParameters of an UmlElement to CodeParameters and adding them to the CodeConstructor or CodeMethod
    ParameterConverterTest
    Tests the ParameterConverter.
    TemplateBindingConverter
    Static class providing methods to convert UmlTemplateBindings to CodeTemplateBindings.
    TemplateBindingConverterTest
    Tests the TemplateBindingConverter.
    TemplateParameterConverter
    Provides static methods to convert UmlTemplateParameters to CodeTemplateParameters and adding them to the CodeParent
    TemplateParameterConverterTest
    Tests TemplateParameterConverter.
